{"url": "https://people.com/movies/naomi-watts-heath-ledger-birthday/", "text": "Naomi Watts paid tribute to former boyfriend Heath Ledger on what would have been the late actor\u2019s 39th birthday.\n\nThe actress, who dated The Dark Knight star from 2002 to 2004, shared a photo of the two holding hands as they walked down a red carpet together.\n\n\u201cHappy birthday to this darling heart,\u201d she wrote on her Instagram Wednesday. \u201cWe will never forget you.\u201d\n\nEarlier this years, Watts, 49, also remembered Ledger on the 10-year anniversary of his death.\n\n\u201cThinking about this beautiful soul today. 10 years ago he left this world. He was a true original,\u201d she wrote at the time. \u201cHeart always on his sleeve, with the most powerful charisma, strength, humor and talent. I will never forget his gentle spirit.\u201d\n\nRELATED VIDEO: See What Made Heath Ledger Such a Compelling Figure \u2014 Even in His Final Days\n\nFollowing their split, Ledger dated Michelle Williams after meeting on the set of their 2005 film Brokeback Mountain and welcomed their daughter Matilda in October 2005. They separated in September 2007.\n\nWatts moved on with actor Liev Schreiber, who she dated for 11 years before breaking up in September 2016.\n\nLedger was found dead on Jan. 22, 2008 in his apartment. He was 28. A toxicology report revealed a fatal mix of prescription drugs in his system. Ledger was survived by his partner at the time, Williams, and his only child, Matilda (now 12).", "images": ["https://peopledotcom.files.wordpress.com/2019/02/julia-stiles.jpg?crop=0px%2C0px%2C1600px%2C840px&resize=1200%2C630", "https://peopledotcom.files.wordpress.com/2018/07/denise-nickerson-2.jpg?crop=0px%2C124px%2C1887px%2C991px&resize=1200%2C630", "https://peopledotcom.files.wordpress.com/2018/01/naomi-watts-heath-ledger.jpg?crop=0px%2C0px%2C1570px%2C824.25px&resize=1200%2C630", "https://peopledotcom.files.wordpress.com/2019/03/gettyimages-1127185398.jpg?crop=0px%2C0px%